`unstable_cache` signature:
```ts
unstable_cache<T>(
  cb: () => Promise<T>,
  keyParts?: string[],
  options?: { tags?: string[], revalidate?: number | false }
): () => Promise<T>
```

This returns a function that caches the result of `cb` based on the key parts and tags. When `revalidateTag("products")` is called, all cached results with the "products" tag are invalidated.

